akland Athletics]], minor-league manager.\n*[[Jeffree Star]], model, fashion designer, makeup artist, DJ, and singer-songwriter.\n*[[Kevin Wasserman]], lead guitarist of [[The Offspring]].<ref name=\"ggusd\">{{cite web|title=Famous People from Pacifica |work=Pacifica School History |publisher=[[Garden Grove Unified School District]]|url=http://www.ggusd.k12.ca.us/phs/files/school_history.html |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919104336/http://www.ggusd.k12.ca.us/phs/files/school_history.html |archivedate=September 19, 2008 }}</ref>\n\n- Roy Park{{div col end}}\n\n==References ==\n{{reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.pacificamariners.com/ Official site of school]\n\n{{Garden Grove, California}}\n{{Orange County, California Schools}}\n\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 1965]]\n[[Category:High schools in Orange County, California]]\n[[Category:Education in Garden Grove, California]]\n[[Category:Public high schools in California]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use mdy dates|date=December 2019}}\n{{Infobox school\n| name = Pacifica High School\n| image = Pacifica HS logo.png\n| image_size = 200px\n| motto = \n| established = 1965\n| type = [[Public school (government funded)|Public]]\n| enrollment = 1,660 (2017\u201318)<ref name=NCES>{{cite web|url=https://nces.ed.gov/ccd/schoolsearch/school_detail.asp?Search=1&DistrictID=0614880&SchoolPageNum=4&ID=061488001868|title=Pacifica High|publisher=National Center for Education Statistics|accessdate=December 1, 2019}}</ref>\n| ratio = 24.06<ref name=NCES/>\n| staff = 69.00 (FTE)<ref name=NCES/>\n| mascot = Sea (Bull)Dog\n| colors = Black, white, and blue\n| conference = [[Empire League]]\n| district = [[Garden Grove Unified School District]]\n| superintendent = Gabriela Mafi\n| principal = Steve Osborne<ref>http://www.gghs.us/apps/pages/index.jsp?uREC_ID=566410&type=u&pREC_ID=865601</ref>\n| streetaddress = 6851 Lampson Avenue\n| city = [[Garden Grove, California|Garden Grove]]\n| 